[76.400711, "o", "\r\n"]
[76.401139, "o", "\u001b[1m  Reason:  \u001b[22mSSM port forwarding: localhost:8443 → EKS cluster endpoint:443 via EksManagementInstance\r\n\u001b[1m  Command: \u001b[22m\u001b[32maws ssm start-session --target i-34ea92b26fa8adc30 --document-name AWS-StartPortForwardingSessionToRemoteHost --parameters '{\"host\":[\"F4B259650994E585A2D7D1556C18741C.gr7.eu-central-1.eks.amazonaws.com\"],\"portNumber\":[\"443\"],\"localPortNumber\":[\"8443\"]}' --profile abc-kubernetes-platform-dev\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[1m  Mode:    \u001b[22m\u001b[33minteractive\u001b[39m (your terminal will be connected to the command)\r\n"]
